caption.body: In the course of rethinking, redesigning, and altering our perception of public and private space, Isamu Noguchi made contributions to world culture that are incalculably influential in their breadth and diffusion.  Thank you to The Isamu Noguchi Foundation and Garden Museum for their generous loan. See "Isamu Noguchi: Inside and Out" on display, pre-security, in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/NoguchiSFO
